Left arrow key:    rotate left
Right arrow key:   rotate right
Up arrow key:	   moves forward	
Down arrow key:	   move backward
F9: 		   headlights	
',', '.' ; B,V :   Rotate camera
C,X : 		   Rotate Lights
PageUp, PageDown : Zoom
Home, Delete :     Switch stationary (directional lights) off or on
Right Control:     Change Camera
Left Control(keep pressed): Switch to robot mode
